## ⛓️ Workflows Automáticos

### PulseScheduler (300s)
```
auto-governance → compliance gaps → KPI compute → file scan (ruff+mypy) 
→ integrity (YAML+MDC+Secrets) → bias check → handoff auto 
→ semantic health → kaizen log → ALCOA check → auto-submit 
→ semantic boot → self-healing
```

### Gateway (toda ação MCP)
```
validate_action → CPC Digital → _fallback_validate (28 checks) 
→ _check_critical_hooks (35 H hooks) → _check_per_action (30+ rules) 
→ CentralWatcher record → claim validator
```

### CICLO 2 (submit / file change)
```
ruff → semantic (3W) → yaml validate → secret scan 
→ mypy → pyright → handoff → RCA → catalog → roadmap
```

